{"tid":1419615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職工盟推算全港昨日約35萬人罷工　認為有鼓勵作用","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:41:26.000Z","uid":212626,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15e6d69b3b78653e8edf21c28e6e75667ccfe24a","tid":1419615,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:03:25.000Z","msg":"全港7個地區昨日舉行罷工集會。職工盟主席吳敏兒在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，推算全港的罷工人數共約35萬人，而參與集會的人數約29萬人，認為有關數字值得留意及帶有鼓勵作用。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，很難預測未來會否再有相關行動，指罷工行動都需要學習及實習。<br />\n<br />\n她形容，航空業的罷工情況較「突出」，以她所知，國泰航空一日需要約3千人上班，但昨日已經有約1500人參與罷工；而國泰港龍航空一日需要約900人上班，昨有約500人參與罷工。至於控制塔亦有部分員工罷工，導致多班航班需要取消，對整個罷工行動有指標作用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472974-20190806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472974-20190806.htm&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKcvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=61368b82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472974-20190806.htm&h=11729dff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472974-20190806.htm</a>"},{"pid":"478dad484b800262ccf2fcfd2749b7779d9b16f2","tid":1419615,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017b1ea0f9c657d1cd08e90bd9d7516a9a194b88","tid":1419615,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a561af6704fc674fe6525a350c50a1a2cc27be6","tid":1419615,"uid":181649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:05:22.000Z","msg":"即係估計9%左右人罷工"},{"pid":"b9616b1e074d43b7f90d71777f1f89107c28924c","tid":1419615,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c